{"tid":2140604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：7月為香港有記錄以來最熱一個月 雨量僅為正常值33%","createTime":"2020-08-05T06:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T07:48:27.000Z","uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"687a2fda5ea8403053cdb5b0eedc9cfba84b40c2","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4993122/org/c1d6567a771aec35ce9a175d0a218926.jpg/6W8U3EruN02h_Skx_Bha6j-WzMGvjiYd7N3hQOzd4UA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4993122%2Forg%2Fc1d6567a771aec35ce9a175d0a218926.jpg%2F6W8U3EruN02h_Skx_Bha6j-WzMGvjiYd7N3hQOzd4UA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d8cd352f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>香港最熱的一個月<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  由於較正常強的副熱帶高壓脊於本月大部分時間持續影響華南，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">二○二○年七月是本港自一八八四年有記錄以來最熱的月份。</span></span>本月平均最高氣溫33.3度、平均氣溫30.2度及平均最低氣溫28.3度，<span class=\"red\">分別較正常值高1.9度、1.4度及1.5度，均為有記錄以來相關月平均值的最高記錄。</span>二○二○年七月的熱夜數目達21天，是有記錄以來最多熱夜數目的月份。由七月五日開始的連續11個熱夜，亦刷新了七月份最長連續熱夜記錄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />此外，本月的酷熱天氣日數為20天，是有記錄以來的單月最高。由於天氣持續晴朗，本月亦遠較正常少雨，全月總雨量只得125.4毫米，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">約為正常值376.5毫米的百分之三十三。</span></span>本年首七個月的累積雨量為1088.8毫米，<ins><span class=\"red\">較同期正常值1473.3毫米少約百分之二十六。</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n  受一道廣闊低壓槽及隨後的偏南氣流影響，本月首三天香港天氣夾雜陽光及驟雨，間中有雷暴。七月三日的大驟雨為本港大部分地區帶來超過10毫米雨量。在高空反氣旋支配下，七月四日至八日除有幾陣驟雨外，本港日間普遍天晴及酷熱。受一股達強風程度的西南氣流影響，隨後兩天本港雲量較多及局部地區有驟雨。<br />\n <br />\n  隨着副熱帶高壓脊由太平洋向西伸展覆蓋中國東南部，七月十一日至七月三十日除有幾陣驟雨外，本港天氣持續天晴及酷熱。其間酷熱天氣更於七月十七日、二十一日、二十二日及二十七日至二十九日觸發局部地區雷暴。在陽光充沛及微風情況下，七月二十三日香港天文台錄得的氣溫上升至全月最高的35.3度。在持續高溫下，酷熱天氣警告在七月十一日至三十日期間維持達467小時，是自二○○○年推出該警告信號以來的最長生效時間記錄。同時，位於南海的季風低壓在本月最後一天逐漸發展為一熱帶低氣壓，其外圍雨帶為香港帶來狂風驟雨及雷暴。當日本港大部分地區錄得超過20毫米雨量，而香港島的雨量更超過40毫米。<span class=\"red\">在大風及驟雨天氣下，持續影響本港超過半個月的酷熱及少雨情況終於得以紓緩。</span><br />\n <br />\n  二○二○年七月有兩個熱帶氣旋影響南海及北太平洋西部。<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月4日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間17時15分</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/04/P2020080400481.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202008%2F04%2FP2020080400481.htm&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeanhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=16a6ccff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/04/P2020080400481.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200715/_2020071508234275414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200715%2F_2020071508234275414.jpg&h=155dd654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200715/photo/bkn-20200715022857030-0715_00822_001_02b.jpg?20200715172151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200715022857030-0715_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20200715172151&h=95c3e326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200715/photo/bkn-20200715022857030-0715_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200715172151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200715022857030-0715_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200715172151&h=cddd4a0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17ca4f7f67078ca1f58cac80fe4797aa3711e242","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"1981-2010 年香港降雨量的月平均值<br />\n七月 376.5<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">二零二零年七月 125.4</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200726/photo/bkn-20200726143926280-0726_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200726192912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200726%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200726143926280-0726_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200726192912&h=5da320db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20200710/photo/bkn-20200710081805586-0710_00942_001_01p.jpg?20200710083136\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20200710%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200710081805586-0710_00942_001_01p.jpg%3F20200710083136&h=53c2e5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200726/photo/bkn-20200726143926280-0726_00822_001_02b.jpg?20200726192912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200726%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200726143926280-0726_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20200726192912&h=05bd89f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aee22e6d11b8613af5bbeaab2c0c5479572ed55","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"肉食者鄙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200730/365521202598514688.jpeg/5FaEdaXlrGLeDPcDvvnVFjM0-np86Wdh9IYog-6GKIM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200730%2F365521202598514688.jpeg%2F5FaEdaXlrGLeDPcDvvnVFjM0-np86Wdh9IYog-6GKIM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dc36ab4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365228917826654208.jpeg/PuMEGCPU9rlQD_xYhsuQL6h3pMh6uJksD5QSFQ-UEhU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365228917826654208.jpeg%2FPuMEGCPU9rlQD_xYhsuQL6h3pMh6uJksD5QSFQ-UEhU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e6ed171d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365153652773621760.jpeg/8AZFyQfw9XJE09RAdAoFNgT41AAaQiWmObuYSi-7mEo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365153652773621760.jpeg%2F8AZFyQfw9XJE09RAdAoFNgT41AAaQiWmObuYSi-7mEo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5c16e45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4984182/org/a275ce6c8b1b752bb27e8989c66f39c8.jpg/GC9L5o9WrA4xfX102seX0ZFzJ7MJkm-80o03VfiNN1U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4984182%2Forg%2Fa275ce6c8b1b752bb27e8989c66f39c8.jpg%2FGC9L5o9WrA4xfX102seX0ZFzJ7MJkm-80o03VfiNN1U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ce97d95f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fb6f6ce0b184b7bc4b10fc839aa61d867075eb2","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"2020年7月25日<br />\n康文署發言人說，進入已封閉的泳灘是違法行為，可被檢控。署方職員今日在巡察各泳灘期間，<span class=\"red\">共發出超過1 500次口頭勸諭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦曾尋求警方協助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 康樂及文化事務署（康文署）今日（七月二十六日）宣布，因應2019冠狀病毒病的最新情況，康文署轄下所有刊憲泳灘已經關閉。泳灘的沖身設施、更衣室及洗手間亦已暫停開放。<span class=\"red\">進入已封閉的沙灘是違法行為。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57113ba51f265c060c91d89f220ce038c81d040","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4929515/org/8551b8e42f9498f98ef24c22eade98e4.jpg/H0TltbOZZcV-BjQ9_8_EAjnEe_1y1U9jw3D7OcNw-zk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4929515%2Forg%2F8551b8e42f9498f98ef24c22eade98e4.jpg%2FH0TltbOZZcV-BjQ9_8_EAjnEe_1y1U9jw3D7OcNw-zk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=efad7ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泳灘有如難民營，政府把所有沖涼設施關閉，成身沙的泳客只有全部谷曬去廁所&mdash;&mdash; 「拖泥帶水」地在洗手盆用水樽裝水沖涼，粗口聲四起，搞到洗手盆、坑渠全部淤塞，於是清潔阿叔粗口聲又起，人人只有幾厘米距離，比雅蘭中心那一班&mdash;&mdash;「慶回歸、中武肺」的組群更加高危！<br />\n<br />\n為什麼綠狗又不去廁所門口舉旗警告&mdash;&mdash;「你們全部衰599G，你哋立即着返泳褲出嚟，否則警方可以射催淚彈」⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f2539f5c739b2cc7c919f1e4deb3995bd1a19d45","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"2020-07-28 <br />\n堂食最後一天 酒樓廚師炸鹹水角釀火警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">牛池灣彩雲商場一酒樓發生火警，今（28 日）中午12時許，警方接報彩雲商場內「好彩酒樓」煙囪冒火及有濃煙。消防派出搜救隊到場處理，由地面拖喉至二樓救火，至中午12時19分將火撲熄，意外中沒有人受傷，約100名人士自行疏散。<br />\n<br />\n因疫情持續爆發，政府推出新一輪防疫措施，周三起全港餐廳禁止堂食，今日為可以堂食的最後一天，豈料酒樓遇上火警，食材盡毀，負責人無奈嘆「屋漏偏逢連夜雨」。 <br />\n<br />\n火撲熄後，現場仍有濃烈燶味，有酒樓職員稱，事發時有廚師正炸鹹水角，懷疑不留神導致火警發生，「救唔到，好大火」。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名職員黎小姐事發時正在廚房沖茶，突然見到火光熊熊，其他同事立即用水將部分火撲滅，當時有大量濃煙冒出，經理於是吩咐其他職員立即安排食客離開酒樓。黎小姐稱，部分食客雖然未埋單，但都要求他們離開，「人命緊要，梗係叫佢走先，唔好再停留係到。」<br />\n<br />\n事發後，有未付款的食客特地返回酒樓，交回點心紙埋單，職員對此感到窩心。<br />\n<br />\n酒樓負責人聶唐稱，酒樓今日無法繼續營業，樓面燒毀的情況不嚴重，主要是廚房內煮食點心的機器、食材燒毀了，相信損失數十萬。今日是堂食的最後一天，卻發生了火警，聶唐直言「呢啲咪就係屋漏偏逢連夜雨，福無雙至，禍不單行。」酒樓明日起便要暫停營業，聶唐慨歎過去一年經濟下滑加上疫情肆虐，集團虧蝕達九千萬元，而起火酒樓未來兩周預計要暫時停業裝修，讓員工放無薪假。由於集團已向政府申領保就業抗疫基金，他解釋員工只是暫時放假，並非不發薪及裁員，不會違規，基於社會責任，集團不希望裁員，大家共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n茶客黃伯每天均會到酒樓飲茶，今日因火警無法前往飲茶，明日開始禁堂食，他嘆「<span class=\"red\">無辦法啦，返屋企煮包麵食。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」其他有飲茶習慣的街坊亦稱，明日起沒有堂食，只好自己買多些菜，自行煮食。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"64e32a14a8f83d62d362900066674c0553cc9646","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb6f6ce0b184b7bc4b10fc839aa61d867075eb2","tid":2140604,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"2020年7月25日<br />\n康文署發言人說，進入已封閉的泳灘是違法行為，可被檢控。署方職員今日在巡察各泳灘期間，<span class=\"red\">共發出超過1 500次口頭勸諭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦曾尋求警方協助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 康樂及文化事務署（康文署）今日（七月二十六日）宣布，因應2019冠狀病毒病的最新情況，康文署轄下所有刊憲泳灘已經關閉。泳灘的沖身設施、更衣室及洗手間亦已暫停開放。<span class=\"red\">進入已封閉的沙灘是違法行為。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》獲授權人員<a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/o